What we do
We help companies in maximizing their protability by implementing
customer-driven business models that align deliveries with customer
expectations and willingness to pay.
Why Visma companies should work with us
We use Visma specic knowledge and apply frameworks from a wide
range of projects across companies. This enables us to oer
industry-approved practices built on the Visma approach
How we achieve it
We provide value by eliminating assumptions through scientically
uncovering customer decision- and value drivers to better adapt roles,
processes, deliveries and pricing accordingly.
